title: Reveal Unclaimed Goobers
body:
Reasoning: Achieving fully revealed collection status would allow The Goobers to be verified on OpenSea and listed on rarity.tools. Initially, we allocated 5,000 Goobers to be paid for in $CLU and then claimed by paying $ETH gas fees for minting. At the time of writing this, 632 Goobers have been paid for in $CLU but have not been revealed. 

Timeline: Unclaimed Goobers would be revealed 48 hours after a positive conclusion to this vote.

Cost: There are no costs associated with this decision. 

Options: 
Option 1
Yes - Reveal all unclaimed Goobers. (A reveal would take place 48 hours after the conclusion of this vote if the DAO votes to reveal.)

Option 2
No - Leave all unclaimed Goobers unrevealed.
author: 0xcE1bb65eB4F7BCd2BB9DB3Cb982b524aB1Fa21a0
